data.description: Location & privacy is what's appreciated along with a spacious property, comfortable home & detached 24X36 shop. Enjoy a cool glass of iced tea while visiting with guest on your 2 covered decks.  Large fenced in garden area along with apple trees, grapes, blueberries & cherries. Many update throughout w/ large living spaces. Newer siding & paint. Shop has concrete floor & attached green house. Convenient landscaping for privacy & just a short distance to the Santiam River. Can be easily converted to 3 brm.
